1:1 Umwami Dawidi yari ashaje ageze mu za bukuru, bakamworosa imyenda ntasusurukirwe.
1:2 Nuko abagaragu be baramubwira bati “Mwami nyagasani, bagushakire umukobwa w'inkumi abane nawe, ajye agukuyakuya agupfumbate, kugira ngo ususurukirwe, nyagasani.”
1:3 Nuko bashaka umukobwa mwiza mu bihugu byose bya Isirayeli, babona Abisagi w'i Shunemu bamuzanira umwami.
1:4 Uwo mukobwa yari mwiza cyane, akajya akuyakuya umwami amukorera, ariko umwami ntiyamumenya.
1:5   Hanyuma Adoniya mwene Hagiti arikuza ati “Nzaba umwami.” Yitunganiriza amagare n'abagendera ku mafarashi, n'abagabo mirongo itanu bo kujya bagenda imbere ye, baca isibo.
1:6 Icyakora se ntabwo yigeze kumucyaha byatuma arakara ati “Ibyo wabitewe n'iki?” Adoniya yari umuntu w'uburanga cyane, kandi yavutse akurikira Abusalomu mwa se.
1:7 Bukeye ajya inama na Yowabu mwene Seruya na Abiyatari umutambyi, baramukurikira bamutiza amaboko.
1:8 Ariko Sadoki umutambyi na Benaya mwene Yehoyada na Natani umuhanuzi, na Shimeyi na Reyi za ntwari za Dawidi, bo ntibaragahuza na Adoniya.
1:9 Hanyuma Adoniya yenda inka n'intama bibyibushye abyicira ku gitare cy'i Zoheleti hateganye na Enirogeli, ararika bene se, abana b'umwami bose, n'Abayuda bose b'abagaragu b'umwami.
1:10 Ariko umuhanuzi Natani na Benaya na za ntwari, na Salomo mwene se, bo ntiyabararika.
1:11   Maze Natani abwira Batisheba nyina wa Salomo ati “Ntiwumvise ko Adoniya mwene Hagiti yiyimitse kandi databuja Dawidi atabizi?
1:12 Nuko none ndakwinginze, ngwino nkugire inama kugira ngo ukize amagara yawe n'ay'umuhungu wawe Salomo.
1:13 Dore genda usange Umwami Dawidi umubwire uti ‘Mwami nyagasani ntiwarahiye umuja wawe uti: Ni ukuri, umuhungu wawe Salomo azima maze gutanga. Kandi uti: Ni we uzima ingoma yanjye? None ni iki gitumye Adoniya yimye?’
1:14 Nuko ukivugana n'umwami nanjye ndi bwinjire ngukurikire, mpamye amagambo yawe.”
1:15 Nuko Batisheba asanga umwami aho yari ari ku murere, ariko umwami yari ashaje cyane, kandi Abisagi w'i Shunemu yabaga aho amukorera.
1:16 Batisheba arunama aramya umwami. Umwami aramubaza ati “Hari icyo ushaka?”
1:17 Aramusubiza ati “Nyagasani, warahiye Uwiteka Imana yawe, ubwira umuja wawe uti ‘Ni ukuri umuhungu wawe Salomo ni we uzima maze gutanga, akicara ku ntebe y'ubwami bwanjye.’
1:18 Ariko none mwami nyagasani, Adoniya yimye utabizi.
1:19 Ubu yishe inka n'intama by'imishishe byinshi cyane, ararika abana b'umwami bose na Abiyatari umutambyi na Yowabu umugaba w'ingabo, ariko umugaragu wawe Salomo ntiyamuraritse.
1:20 Nuko none mwami nyagasani, Abisirayeli bose baguteze amaso ngo ubamenyeshe ūzima ingoma yawe, umaze gutanga.
1:21 Kandi dore mwami nyagasani, numara gutanga ugasanga ba sogokuruza, utabigenjeje utyo jyewe n'umuhungu wanjye Salomo twakwitwa abagome.”
1:22 Akivugana n'umwami, umuhanuzi Natani arinjira.
1:23 Babwira umwami bati “Nguyu umuhanuzi Natani araje.” Ageze imbere y'umwami amwikubita imbere yubamye.
1:24 Natani abaza umwami ati “Harya, mwami nyagasani, ni wowe wavuze ngo Adoniya ni we uzima umaze gutanga, akicara ku ntebe y'ubwami?
1:25 Dore uyu munsi yamanutse yica inka n'intama by'imishishe byinshi cyane, ararika abana b'umwami bose n'abatware b'ingabo na Abiyatari umutambyi, ubu bararya baranywera imbere ye, bavuga ngo ‘Umwami Adoniya aragahoraho.’
1:26 Ariko jyewe umugaragu wawe na Sadoki umutambyi, na Benaya mwene Yehoyada n'umugaragu wawe Salomo ntiyaturaritse.
1:27 Mbese ibyo byabaye ku itegeko ry'umwami databuja, kandi utabwiye abagaragu bawe ūzicara ku ntebe y'umwami databuja, umaze gutanga?”
1:28 Umwami aramubwira ati “Mpamagarira Batisheba.” Baramuhamagara aritaba, ahagarara imbere y'umwami.
1:29 Nuko umwami ararahira ati “Nk'uko Uwiteka ahoraho, wacunguye amagara yanjye mu byago byose,
1:30 uko nakurahiye Uwiteka Imana ya Isirayeli nti ‘Ni ukuri umuhungu wawe Salomo ni we uzima maze gutanga, akicara ku ntebe y'ubwami mu cyimbo cyanjye’, ni ukuri ni ko ndi bubitegeke uyu munsi.”
1:31 Batisheba yunama imbere y'umwami aramuramya, aravuga ati “Umwami nyagasani aragahoraho.”
1:32 Umwami Dawidi aravuga ati “Nimumpamagarire Sadoki umutambyi, n'umuhanuzi Natani na Benaya mwene Yehoyada.” Bitaba umwami.
1:33 Nuko umwami arababwira ati “Mujyane n'abagaragu ba shobuja, kandi muhekeshe umuhungu wanjye Salomo ku yanjye nyumbu, mumanukane na we mujye i Gihoni.
1:34 Nuko umutambyi Sadoki n'umuhanuzi Natani nibagerayo, bamwimikishirizeyo amavuta abe umwami wa Isirayeli, maze muvuze ikondera muti ‘Umwami Salomo aragahoraho.’
1:35 Muhereko muzamuke mumukurikiye aze yicare ku ntebe y'ubwami bwanjye, kuko azaba umwami mu cyimbo cyanjye, kandi ari we nategetse kuba umwami w'Abisirayeli n'uw'Abayuda.”
1:36 Nuko Benaya mwene Yehoyada asubiza umwami ati “Amen. Uwiteka Imana y'umwami databuja na yo ibihamye.
1:37 Nk'uko Uwiteka yabanaga n'umwami databuja abe ari ko azabana na Salomo, akomeze ingoma ye kugira ngo irushe iy'umwami databuja gukomera.”
1:38 Nuko umutambyi Sadoki n'umuhanuzi Natani na Benaya mwene Yehoyada, n'Abakereti n'Abapeleti baramanuka bahekesha Salomo ku nyumbu y'Umwami Dawidi, bamujyana i Gihoni.
1:39 Umutambyi Sadoki aherako akura ihembe ry'amavuta mu ihema ayimikisha Salomo, maze bavuza ikondera abantu bose bashyira ejuru bati “Umwami Salomo aragahoraho.”
1:40 Nuko abantu bose bazamuka bamukurikiye bavuza imyironge, baranezerwa cyane isi irasaduka ku bw'urusaku rwabo.
1:41 Maze Adoniya n'abo yari yararitse bari kumwe bose barabyumva, bari bakimara kurya. Yowabu yumvise ijwi ry'ikondera aravuga ati “Se ariko urwo rusaku ni urw'iki ko umurwa uvurunganye?”
1:42 Akibivuga haza Yonatani mwene Abiyatari umutambyi, Adoniya aramubwira ati “Injira kuko uri umuntu ukomeye kandi uzanye inkuru nziza.”
1:43 Yonatani abwira Adoniya ati “Ni ukuri, Umwami Dawidi databuja yimitse Salomo ngo abe umwami.
1:44 Kandi umwami yamwohereje hamwe na Sadoki umutambyi, n'umuhanuzi Natani na Benaya mwene Yehoyada, n'Abakereti n'Abapeleti bamuhekesha ku nyumbu y'umwami.
1:45 Sadoki umutambyi n'umuhanuzi Natani bamwimikiye i Gihoni, ubu barazamutse banezerewe bituma umurwa urangīra. Ni rwo urwo rusaku mwumva.
1:46 None ubu Salomo yicaye ku ntebe y'ubwami.
1:47 Kandi abagaragu b'umwami baje basabira Umwami Dawidi databuja umugisha bati ‘Imana yawe ikuze izina rya Salomo kurirutisha iryawe, kandi ikomeze ingoma ye kugira ngo irushe iyawe gukomera.’ Umwami aherako yunama ku gisasiro cye
1:48 aravuga ati ‘Uwiteka Imana ya Isirayeli ihimbazwe, kuko ari yo itanze uwo kwicara ku ntebe yanjye nkirora.’ ”
1:49 Maze abo Adoniya yari yararitse baratinya, barahaguruka baragenda umuntu wese aca ukwe.
1:50 Nuko Adoniya atinya Salomo, arahaguruka aragenda yisunga amahembe y'icyotero.
1:51 Nuko bajya kubwira Salomo bati “Adoniya yatinye Umwami Salomo ubu yisunze amahembe y'icyotero, ariho aravuga ngo ‘Icyampa Umwami Salomo akandahira uyu munsi ko atazanyicisha inkota jyewe umugaragu we.’ ”
1:52 Nuko Salomo aravuga ati “Niyerekana ko ari umuntu mwiza nta gasatsi ke kazagwa hasi, ariko nabonekwaho n'icyaha azapfa.”
1:53 Umwami Salomo aherako yohereza abo kumukura ku cyotero. Araza aramya Umwami Salomo. Salomo aramubwira ati “Itahire.”
2:1 Igihe cya Dawidi cyo gutanga cyenda gusohora, yihanangiriza umuhungu we Salomo aramubwira ati
2:2 “Ubu ndagiye nk'uko ab'isi bose bagenda. Nuko komera ugaragaze ko uri umugabo.
2:3 Ujye wumvira ibyo Uwiteka Imana yawe yakwihanangirije: ni ko kugendera mu nzira zayo, ukitondera amategeko yayo n'ibyo yategetse, n'amateka n'ibyo yahamije nk'uko byanditswe mu mategeko ya Mose, kugira ngo ubashishwe ibyo uzakora byose aho uzagana hose,
2:4 kugira ngo Uwiteka azakomeze ijambo rye yamvuzeho ati ‘Abana bawe nibirindira mu ngeso zabo nziza, bakagendera imbere yanjye mu by'ukuri n'imitima yabo yose n'ubugingo bwabo bwose, ntuzabura uzungura ingoma ya Isirayeli.’ Uko ni ko Imana yavuze.
2:5  “Kandi uzi ibyo Yowabu mwene Seruya yangiriye, n'ibyo yagiriye abagaba bombi b'ingabo za Isirayeli: Abuneri mwene Neri na Amasa mwene Yeteri, ko yabishe akavusha amaraso nk'ayo mu ntambara mu gihe cy'amahoro, akayasīga ku mukandara akenyeje no ku nkweto yari akwese.
2:6 Nuko uzamugenze uko uzigira inama, ntuzemere ko imvi ze zimanuka amahoro zijya mu mva.
2:7  “Ariko bene Barizilayi w'Umunyagaleyadi uzabagirire neza, bazajye basangira n'abarira ku meza yawe, kuko ari ko bangiriye igihe nari narahunze mwene so Abusalomu.
2:8  “Kandi ufite Shimeyi mwene Gera w'Umubenyamini w'i Bahurimu, wamvumye umuvumo mubi umunsi najyaga i Mahanayimu, ariko hanyuma ansanganirira kuri Yorodani murahira Uwiteka nti ‘Sinzakwicisha inkota.’
2:9 Ariko rero ntuzamubare nk'utariho urubanza, kuko uri umunyabwenge uzamenye uko ukwiriye kumugirira, kandi uzamanure imvi ze zijye mu mva ziriho amaraso wamuvushije.”
2:10 Nuko Dawidi aratanga asanga ba sekuruza, bamuhamba mu mudugudu wa Dawidi.
2:11  Kandi imyaka Dawidi yamaze ku ngoma ategeka Abisirayeli yari mirongo ine, kuko yamaze imyaka irindwi ategeka i Heburoni, akamara n'indi mirongo itatu n'itatu i Yerusalemu.
2:12  Nuko Salomo asubira ku ngoma ya se Dawidi, ubwami bwe burakomezwa cyane.
2:13 Bukeye Adoniya mwene Hagiti asanga Batisheba nyina wa Salomo. Batisheba aramubaza ati “Uzanywe n'amahoro?” Na we ati “Ni amahoro.”
2:14 Kandi ati “Hari icyo nshaka kukubwira.” Umugabekazi ati “Mbwira.”
2:15 Aramubwira ati “Uzi ko ubwami bwari ubwanjye, kuko Abisirayeli bose bari bampanze amaso ngo mbe umwami. Ariko hanyuma burahinduka buba ubwa mwene data, kuko yabuhawe n'Uwiteka.
2:16 Ariko none hari icyo ngusaba ntukinyime.” Aramusubiza ati “Kivuge.”
2:17  Aramubwira ati “Ndakwinginze nsabira Umwami Salomo (kuko atabasha kukwima), anshyingire Abisagi w'i Shunemu.”
2:18 Batisheba aramubwira ati “Nuko ndakuvugira ku mwami.”
2:19 Batisheba aherako asanga Umwami Salomo ngo avugire Adoniya ibye. Nuko umwami amubonye ahagurutswa no kumusanganira, aramwunamira asubira ku ntebe y'ubwami, ategeka ko bazana intebe y'umugabekazi. Nuko umugabekazi yicara iburyo bwa Salomo.
2:20 Nuko aravuga ati “Hari icyo ngusaba gito ntukinyime.” Umwami aramusubiza ati “Nsaba Mubyeyi wanjye, sinakwima.”
2:21 Aramubwira ati “Reka dushyingire mwene so Adoniya, Abisagi w'i Shunemu.”
2:22 Nuko Umwami Salomo asubiza nyina ati “Ni iki gituma usabira Adoniya Abisagi w'i Shunemu? Erega wamusabira n'ubwami kuko ari mukuru wanjye, yego! Kandi ugasabira na Abiyatari umutambyi, na Yowabu mwene Seruya.”
2:23 Umwami Salomo arahira Uwiteka ati “Niba ijambo Adoniya avuze atari iryo kumwicisha, Imana izabimpore ndetse bikabije.
2:24 Nuko rero ndahiye Uwiteka uhoraho wankomeje, akanshyira ku ngoma ya data Dawidi, akampa inzu idakuka nk'uko yasezeranye, ni ukuri uyu munsi Adoniya baramwica.”
2:25 Nuko Umwami Salomo yohereza Benaya mwene Yehoyada, aramusumira aramwica.
2:26  Kandi umwami abwira Abiyatari umutambyi ati “Hoshi, igendere wigire Anatoti mu gikingi cyawe, kuko wari ukwiriye gupfa ariko sindi bukwice muri iki gihe, kuko wajyaga uheka isanduku y'Uwiteka Imana imbere y'umukambwe wanjye Dawidi, kandi kuko wababaranaga na we mu byamubabaje byose.”
2:27  Uko ni ko Salomo yakuye Abiyatari mu butambyi bw'Uwiteka, kugira ngo asohoze ijambo Uwiteka yavugiye i Shilo ku nzu ya Eli.
2:28 Nuko inkuru igera kuri Yowabu, kandi Yowabu yari yarakurikiye Adoniya nubwo atakurikiye Abusalomu. Yowabu abyumvise ahungira mu Ihema ry'Uwiteka, yisunga amahembe y'icyotero.
2:29 Hanyuma babwira Umwami Salomo bati “Yowabu yahungiye mu Ihema ry'Uwiteka, ubu ari ku cyotero.” Nuko Salomo yohereza Benaya mwene Yehoyada aramubwira ati “Genda umwice.”
2:30 Benaya aherako aragenda ajya mu Ihema ry'Uwiteka, aramubwira ati “Umwami aravuze ngo ‘Sohoka.’ ” Na we aramusubiza ati “Oya ahubwo ndagwa aha.” Benaya aragenda abwira umwami ati “Uku ni ko Yowabu ambwiye kandi ni ko anshubije.”
2:31 Umwami aramubwira ati “Ubigenze uko yavuze, umwice umuhambe kugira ngo ukure kuri jye no ku nzu y'umukambwe wanjye, amaraso Yowabu yavushije nta mpamvu.
2:32 Uwiteka araba amuvushije amuhoye ba bantu babiri yasumiye, akabicisha inkota umukambwe wanjye Dawidi atabizi, kandi bari abantu bamuruta ubwiza no gukiranuka: ni bo Abuneri mwene Neri umugaba w'ingabo za Isirayeli, na Amasa mwene Yeteri umugaba w'ingabo z'Abayuda.
2:33 Uko ni ko amaraso yabo azahorerwa Yowabu n'urubyaro rwe iteka ryose, ariko Dawidi n'urubyaro rwe n'inzu ye n'ingoma ye bizagira amahoro avuye ku Uwiteka iminsi yose.”
2:34 Nuko Benaya mwene Yehoyada asubirayo aramusumira amutsinda aho. Bamuhamba mu rugo rwe bwite aho yari atuye mu butayu.
2:35 Hanyuma umwami ashyira Benaya mwene Yehoyada mu cyimbo cye, ngo abe umugaba w'ingabo. Kandi umwami ashyira Sadoki umutambyi mu cyimbo cya Abiyatari.
2:36 Bukeye umwami atumira Shimeyi aramubwira ati “Wiyubakire inzu i Yerusalemu uyigumemo, ntuzayivemo ngo ugire ahandi ujya.
2:37 Umunsi wavuyeyo ukambuka akagezi Kidironi, uzamenye neza ko utazabura gupfa. Amaraso yawe azabe ari wowe abaho.”
2:38 Shimeyi asubiza umwami ati “Ibyo umbwiye ni byiza. Uko uvuze mwami nyagasani, ni ko umugaragu wawe nzabigenza.” Nuko Shimeyi aba i Yerusalemu ahamara iminsi myinshi.
2:39 Hahise imyaka itatu, abagaragu babiri ba Shimeyi baracika bajya kwa Akishi mwene Māka umwami w'i Gati. Bukeye babwira Shimeyi bati “Abagaragu bawe bari i Gati.”
2:40 Shimeyi arahaguruka ashyira amatandiko ku ndogobe ye, ajya i Gati kwa Akishi gushaka abagaragu be. Nuko Shimeyi aragenda abakura i Gati.
2:41 Hanyuma Salomo abwirwa ko Shimeyi yavuye i Yerusalemu, akajya i Gati akagaruka.
2:42 Umwami atumira Shimeyi aramubwira ati “Harya sinakurahije Uwiteka, nkakwihanangiriza rwose nti ‘Umenye neza ko umunsi wavuyeyo ukagira aho ugana hose, utazabura gupfa’? Ukansubiza uti ‘Ibyo uvuze ni byiza ndabyumvise’?
2:43 None ni iki cyakubujije kwirinda indahiro y'Uwiteka n'itegeko nagutegetse?”
2:44 Umwami arongera abwira Shimeyi ati “Mbese aho uribuka ubugome bwawe bwose umutima wawe wakwemeje, ubwo wagomeye umukambwe wanjye Dawidi? Ni cyo kiri butume Uwiteka aguhora ubugome bwawe.
2:45 Ariko Umwami Salomo we azahabwa umugisha, kandi ingona ya Dawidi izakomezwa imbere y'Uwiteka iminsi yose.”
2:46 Maze umwami ategeka Benaya mwene Yehoyada kumwica, na we arasohoka aramusumira, amutsinda aho. Nuko ubwami bukomezwa mu maboko ya Salomo.
3:1 Salomo yuzura na Farawo umwami wa Egiputa arongora umukobwa we, amuzana mu mudugudu wa Dawidi agumayo kugeza aho Salomo yamariye kubaka inzu ye bwite n'iy'Uwiteka, n'inkike zo kugota i Yerusalemu.
3:2 Icyo gihe abantu batambiraga mu nsengero zo ku tununga, kuko kugeza ubwo hatariho inzu yubakiwe izina ry'Uwiteka.
3:3 Salomo yakundaga Uwiteka akagendera mu mategeko ya se Dawidi, kandi yajyaga atamba ibitambo, akosereza imibavu mu nsengero zo ku tununga.
3:4 Bukeye umwami ajya i Gibeyoni gutambirayo, kuko ari ho akanunga karusha utundi icyubahiro kabaga. Nuko Salomo atambirayo ibitambo byoswa igihumbi.
3:5 Salomo akiri i Gibeyoni Uwiteka amubonekera mu nzozi nijoro. Imana iramubaza iti “Nsaba icyo ushaka nkiguhe.”
3:6 Salomo aravuga ati “Wagiriye data Dawidi ineza nyinshi, kuko yagendanaga ukuri no gukiranuka imbere yawe agutunganiye mu mutima we, kandi wamugeneye kumugirira iyi neza ikomeye, umuha umwana we ngo yicare ku ntebe y'ubwami bwe nk'uko biri none.
3:7 Nuko none, Uwiteka Mana yanjye, wimitse umugaragu wawe mu cyimbo cya data Dawidi, ariko ndi umwana muto sinzi iyo biva n'iyo bijya.
3:8 Kandi umugaragu wawe ndi hagati y'abantu bawe watoranyije, b'ubwoko bukomeye butabarika.
3:9 Nuko rero, uhe umugaragu wawe umutima ujijutse ngo nshobore gucira abantu bawe imanza, kugira ngo menye gutandukanya ibyiza n'ibibi. Mbese ni nde washobora gucira ubu bwoko bwawe bukomeye imanza?”
3:10 Maze ayo magambo anezeza Uwiteka, kuko ari yo Salomo yamusabye.
3:11 Imana iherako ibwira Salomo iti “Kuko ibyo ari byo usabye ukaba udasabye kurama, ntusabe n'ubutunzi cyangwa ko abanzi bawe bapfa, ahubwo ukisabira ubwenge bwo kumenya guca imanza zitabera,
3:12 nuko nkugiriye uko unsabye. Dore nguhaye umutima w'ubwenge ujijutse, mu bakubanjirije cyangwa mu bazagukurikira nta wuzahwana nawe.
3:13 Kandi nguhaye n'ibyo utansabye, ubutunzi n'icyubahiro bizatuma nta mwami n'umwe wo mu bandi bami uzahwana nawe, iminsi yose yo kubaho kwawe.
3:14 Nuko kandi nugendera mu nzira zanjye, ukitondera amateka n'amategeko yanjye nk'uko so Dawidi yazigenderagamo, nzakongerera kurama.”
3:15 Maze Salomo aribambura amenya ko yarotaga. Bukeye asubira i Yerusalemu, ahageze ahagarara imbere y'isanduku y'isezerano ry'Uwiteka ahatambira ibitambo byoswa, n'iby'ishimwe yuko ari amahoro, hanyuma atekeshereza abagaragu be bose ibyokurya.
3:16 Bukeye abagore babiri b'abamalaya basanga umwami, bamuhagarara imbere.
3:17 Umwe muri bo aravuga ati “Nyagasani, nabanaga n'uyu mugore mu nzu imwe, bukeye turi kumwe mu nzu mbyara umwana.
3:18 Maze iminsi itatu mbyaye, uyu mugore na we abyara turi kumwe. Nta mushyitsi wari kumwe natwe muri iyo nzu, keretse twebwe ubwacu.
3:19 Ariko nijoro umwana w'uyu mugore arapfa, azize yuko yamuryamiye.
3:20 Icyo gicuku arabyuka, ankura umwana mu gituza ubwo umuja wawe nari nsinziriye, amuryamisha mu gituza cye, wa wundi wapfuye amuryamisha mu gituza cyanjye.
3:21 Mbyutse mu museke konsa umwana nsanga yapfuye, ariko mu gitondo mwitegereje mbona ko atari umwana wanjye nibyariye.”
3:22 Undi mugore aravuga ati “Oya, umuzima ni we wanjye, uwapfuye ni uwawe.” Uwa mbere ati “Oya, uwapfuye ni uwawe, umuzima ni we wanjye.” Babivugira batyo imbere y'umwami.
3:23 Nuko umwami aravuga ati “Yemwe, umwe agira ati ‘Umuzima ni we wanjye, uwapfuye ni uwawe’, n'undi akagira ati‘ Oya, ahubwo uwapfuye ni uwawe, umuzima ni we wanjye.’ ”
3:24 Umwami ati “Nimunzanire inkota.” Barayimuzanira.
3:25 Maze umwami arategeka ati “Uwo mwana muzima nimumucemo kabiri igice kimwe mugihe umwe, ikindi mugihe undi.”
3:26 Nuko umugore nyina w'umwana muzima wari umufitiye imbabazi, abwira umwami ati “Nyagasani, umuzima mumwihere wimwica, nubwo bimeze bite.” Ariko undi aravuga ati “Ahubwo bamucemo kabiri, mubure nawe umubure.”
3:27 Umwami aherako arategeka ati “Uwo mwana muzima ntimumwice na hato, mumuhe uriya mugore kuko ari we nyina.”
3:28 Nuko Abisirayeli bose bumvise uko umwami yaciye urwo rubanza baramutinya, kuko babonye ko ubwenge bw'Imana bwari muri we bwo guca imanza zitabera.
4:1 Nuko Umwami Salomo aba umwami w'Abisirayeli bose,
