7:8  Kandi inzu yabagamo yo mu gikari haruguru y'iryo baraza na yo yari yubatswe ityo. Kandi Salomo yubaka indi nzu isa n'iy'iryo baraza, ayubakira umukobwa wa Farawo yari yararongoye.
